{
  "stem": "19921.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But it was trade school.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They didn't teach you anything from trade.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "It was called trade school, but they teach you the continuation of the education.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And that has to be done, like, three times a week.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "So I had to continue with that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And it was just too much.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I just had to quit.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "When I quit that, my uncle which I had, he was living in Silesia.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "It was approximately 130 kilometers from my hometown.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "He was a master tailor.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And-- he had to be a master tailor.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "To employ people, you had to be a master tailor.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And to take somebody to apprentice, you had to be a master tailor.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "You couldn't apprentice with anybody else.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Otherwise, you would not get your license.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Now, before I continue, in Europe, you had to apprentice for three years.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "You had to apprentice for three years.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And after that, you had to also work with a master tailor after that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "After the three years, you had to work with a master tailor for about two years-- at least two years.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And then you had to produce a full garment.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "Whichever you choose-- a coat, or a suit, whatever you choose.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "You had to produce that, and it was scrutinized by other master tailors-- critics.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] If the garment was good, then you passed it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "Unfortunately, it was interrupted for me because the war broke out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "In any event, I was living with my uncle.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "His name was Moniek Lehrfeld.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "That's M-O-N-I-E-K Lehrfeld-- L-E-H-R-F-EL-D.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And his wife Helena.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And at that time, they had a little baby which was approximately three or four months old.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And I was living with him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "He had a spacious apartment in upper Silesia.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
